{
  "stem": "21089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he let me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I walk in, I didn't know where-- which office to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I-- first door, I was-- it was in German and in Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A civilian affairs-- adminis-- administrative affairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I say I want to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came, walk in the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Knock on door, walk in the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- by the desk was a German officer, and in the corner, a secretary, also in uniform, a blond German girl.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him what I came here for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he voiced-- a loud voice, said, you know we are in a war with the communists and you came here with such piddly things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know I had the guts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never pound in my life on a table-- never, never.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't pound, but just put my hand on the table and told him, and you want me to come to those people and tell him that you don't want to do-- to denationalize this what communists did it?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They will call me communist, and they will call you communist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I cannot come back to the-- to the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I cannot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So and he saw my serious-- that I--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but when I put my hand on his desk, I knew that he was-- that he was ready to take out the gun and shoot me or something.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So immediately, I start talking about the communists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I wouldn't did that, he would threw me out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what he would do with me because I was dressed like a peasant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the only thing, I had the 3/4 boots like-- like the German was wearing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and so he asked, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I told him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
